{"tid":2172361,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Viutv 99台 韓劇 《附身》8.26星期三起 逢一至五晚 21:30 (1)","createTime":"2020-08-24T14:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T13:32:42.000Z","uid":4643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4181c01a671426043f51ce896a6c1f09e2729e35","tid":2172361,"uid":4643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">Viutv 99台 韓劇 《附身》<br />\n8.26逢星期三起 <br />\n逢星期一至五晚 21:30</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">《附身》（韓語：빙의／憑依 Bingui，英語：Possessed），為韓國OCN於2019年3月6日起播出的水木經典連續劇，由《失業救助羅曼史》的崔道勳導演執導、朴熙江作家執筆，本劇講述邪惡的靈魂附身到人類身體裏進行犯罪，而有着超強直覺的不良刑警－姜必成（宋清晨飾）與擁有超強能力的靈媒－洪書靜（高準熹飾），利用各自的能力一起破案、打擊惡靈們，既驚悚又搞笑的故事。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/18/Possessed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F18%2FPossessed.png&h=496b8f70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e448b7826e881e4c5c1aaf5ed9b037a9253889f","tid":2172361,"uid":4643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb3bbc573e25ab63a4d1688ae94151f25899a88","tid":2172361,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425589570da2b2c47bdf4abaaffb8c6abc2f6e6f","tid":2172361,"uid":319342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:28:34.000Z","msg":"第一集就19禁"},{"pid":"e28c51a2120b2f5bab51cf1dd0473f4c97c68172","tid":2172361,"uid":4643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"推呢個<br />\n<br />\n[ViuTV] 2130~2230 附身。鬼上身？你咁樣係唔會令我驚㗎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://l